When ''Excerpt Tiddler'' has important knowledge points, you can make 
deeper ''Excerpt Tiddler'' for each knowledge point, and edit it to convert it into a ''Question Tiddler''. 

Please refer to [[How to use Q&A, Cloze and Select Question?]] and use <<.icon $:/core/images/underline>> on the edit bar to rewrite the corresponding question template form, then click <<.icon $:/plugins/oflg/fishing-catchfish/icons/setquestion>>, <<.icon $:/plugins/oflg/fishing-catchfish/icons/setcloze>> or <<.icon $:/plugins/oflg/fishing-catchfish/icons/setselect>> to convert it. 